---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />

  <!-- Conteúdo da página Microbioma -->
  <div id="microbioma-content">
    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="pt-BR">
    <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8">
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
      <title>AlphaBioma - Microbioma</title>
     <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4B9AFB;
      --primary-dark: #3B7FD1;
      --secondary: #979df0;
      --dark: #0F172A;
      --light: #F8FAFC;
      --accent: #1a24a7;
    }
      
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #060d19);
        color: var(--light);
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }
      
      .section {
        padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }
      
      /* Hero */
      .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 90vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.8), transparent 70%), linear-gradient(135deg, #08192f, #0b1a2d, #060d19);
        color: white;
      }
      
      .hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.4;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }
      
      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.8);
        max-width: 600px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
        color: var(--dark);
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -5px rgba(86, 53, 177, 0.4);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 100;
      }
      
      
      .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -5px rgba(34, 106, 201, 0.5);
      }
      
      /* Section Titles */
      .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .section-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        background: var(--accent);
        border-radius: 2px;
      }
      
      /* Info Cards */
      .microbiome-content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }
      
      .info-card {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        transition: 0.3s ease;
        color: var(--light);
      }
      
      .info-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        border-color: var(--primary);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      }
      
      .info-card-title {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .info-card-text {
        color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.9);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .highlight-text {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 500;
      }      
        
          .microbiome-section {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom,#0a1c3f, #37568b, #0a1c3f); /* substitui Tailwind: from-black via-blue-950 to-black */
            color: white;
          }

          .microbiome-particles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            /* Aqui você pode adicionar partículas ou efeitos visuais */
          }

          /* Título com destaque */
          .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
          }

          .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--accent, #f472b6); /* rosa se não definido */
            border-radius: 2px;
          }

          /* Grid de cards */
          .microbiome-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
          }
        .info-card {
          background: rgba(5, 26, 75, 0.8);
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
          border: 1px solid rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
          border-radius: 16px;
          padding: 2rem;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          height: 100%;
          transform-style: preserve-3d;
          transform: perspective(1000px);
        }
        
        .info-card:hover {
          transform: perspective(1000px) translateY(-10px) rotateX(5deg);
          border-color: rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.4);
          box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),
                      0 0 30px rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
        }
        
        .info-card-icon {
          width: 60px;
          height: 60px;
          background: rgba(28, 6, 230, 0.5);
          border-radius: 12px;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .info-card-icon svg {
          width: 32px;
          height: 32px;
          fill: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .info-card-title {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          color: white;
        }
        
        .info-card-text {
          color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.9);
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .highlight-text {
          color: var(--white);
          font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        /* ROI Benefits Section */
        .roi-section {
          position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom,#0a1c3f, #37568b, #0a1c3f);; /* substitui Tailwind: from-black via-blue-950 to-black */
            color: rgb(241, 236, 236);
          }
        
        .roi-section::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.1), transparent 70%);
          z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .roi-cards {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
          gap: 2rem;
          margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        .roi-card {
          position: relative;
          background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
          border-radius: 16px;
          padding: 2rem;
          overflow: hidden;
          border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          height: 100%;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .roi-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-10px);
          border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4);
          box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .roi-card::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: -50px;
          right: -50px;
          width: 100px;
          height: 100px;
          background: radial-gradient(var(--primary) 0%, transparent 70%);
          opacity: 0.15;
          filter: blur(20px);
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .roi-card:hover::before {
          opacity: 0.25;
          transform: scale(1.5);
        }
        
        .roi-card-content {
          position: relative;
          z-index: 1;
          flex: 1;
        }
        
        .roi-percentage {
          font-size: 3rem;
          font-weight: 800;
          color: var(--primary);
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .roi-card-title {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          color: white;
        }
        
        .roi-card-text {
          color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
          font-size: 0.95rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Service Process Section */
        .service-timeline {
          padding-top: 4rem;
          position: relative;
        }
        
        .timeline-container {
          position: relative;
          margin-top: 4rem;
        }
        
        .timeline-track {
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: 50%;
          width: 4px;
          height: 100%;
          background: rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
          transform: translateX(-50%);
          z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .timeline-progress {
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          height: 0;
          background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary), var(--accent));
          transition: height 1.5s ease;
          z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .timeline-items {
          position: relative;
          z-index: 3;
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          margin-bottom: 6rem;
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
          transition: all 0.8s ease;
        }
        
        .timeline-item:last-child {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .timeline-item.left {
          flex-direction: row;
        }
        
        .timeline-item.right {
          flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }
        
        .timeline-icon {
          flex: 0 0 120px;
          height: 120px;
          margin: 0 2rem;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          background: rgba(13, 40, 80, 0.5);
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
          border: 2px solid rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.3);
          border-radius: 50%;
          box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 
                      0 0 20px rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.3);
          position: relative;
          overflow: hidden;
          transition: all 0.4s ease;
          transform-style: preserve-3d;
          transform: perspective(1000px);
        }
        
        .timeline-icon::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: -50%;
          left: -50%;
          width: 200%;
          height: 200%;
          background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
          opacity: 0;
          transform: scale(0.5);
          transition: all 0.6s ease;
        }
        
        .timeline-icon:hover {
          transform: perspective(1000px) scale(1.05) rotateY(10deg);
          border-color: rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.8);
          box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 
                      0 0 30px rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.5);
        }
        
        .timeline-icon:hover::before {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: scale(1);
          animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
          flex: 1;
          max-width: calc(50% - 4rem);
          padding: 2rem;
          background: rgba(13, 40, 80, 0.4);
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
          border-radius: 16px;
          border: 1px solid rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
          box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          transition: all 0.4s ease;
          transform-style: preserve-3d;
          transform: perspective(1000px);
        }
        
        .timeline-content:hover {
          transform: perspective(1000px) translateY(-5px) rotateX(5deg);
          border-color: rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.4);
          box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),
                      0 0 20px rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.2);
        }
        
        .timeline-content h3 {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          color: #ffffff;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
        }
        
        .timeline-content h3 span {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          width: 36px;
          height: 36px;
          margin-right: 12px;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
          border-radius: 50%;
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .timeline-content p {
          color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .info-box {
          margin-top: 1.5rem;
          padding: 1rem;
          background: rgba(75, 154, 251, 0.1);
          border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .info-box h4 {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
          color: whitesmoke;
        }
        
        .info-box p {
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
        }
        
        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
          text-align: center;
          padding: 6rem 0;
          position: relative;
          overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .cta-section::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(26, 230, 155, 0.808), transparent 10%);
          z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .cta-content {
          position: relative;
          z-index: 1;
          max-width: 700px;
          margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .cta-title {
          font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
          font-weight: 700;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-text {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.8);
          margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 1rem;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        /* Animations */
        @keyframes pulse {
          0% {
            opacity: 0.4;
          }
          50% {
            opacity: 0.8;
          }
          100% {
            opacity: 0.4;
          }
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
          0% {
            transform: translateY(0);
          }
          50% {
            transform: translateY(-20px);
          }
          100% {
            transform: translateY(0);
          }
        }
        
        /* Mobile responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
          .section {
            padding: 4rem 0;
          }
          
          .timeline-item {
            flex-direction: column !important;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-left: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
          }
          
          .timeline-track {
            left: 1.5rem;
          }
          
          .timeline-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin: 0;
          }
          
          .timeline-icon svg {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
          }
          
          .timeline-content {
            max-width: 100%;
            margin-top: 2rem;
          }
          
          .roi-card {
            height: auto;
          }
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <!-- Hero Section with 3D Microbiome Visualization -->
      <section class="hero-section" >
        <div id="microbiome-canvas"></div>
        <div class="container ">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">Decodificando o microbioma para potencializar seu negócio</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Transforme a complexidade do microbioma animal em resultados mensuráveis com nossa tecnologia avançada de sequenciamento e análise de dados.</p>
            <a href="#microbiome" id="microbiome-button" class="cta-button">Descobrir Como Funciona</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden section-padding">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 blob bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3533c9]/10 to-[#0048b5]/10 blur-3xl animate-float-v"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 blob bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0048b5]/10 to-[#4c7fcb]/10 blur-3xl animate-float-h"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-64 h-64 blob bg-gradient-to-br from-[#215ec3]/10 to-transparent blur-2xl animate-pulse-grow"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- DNA Animation Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottow-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 via-transparent to-black/50 z-12"></div>
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15">
        <source src="/video/dna2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <!-- What is Microbiome Section -->
      <section id="microbiome" class="section microbiome-section section-padding">
        <div class="microbiome-particles" id="particles"></div>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">O que é o microbioma?</h2>
            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-blue-100">Entenda como este ecossistema invisível impacta diretamente seus resultados financeiros</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="microbiome-content">
            <div class="info-card">
              <div class="info-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="info-card-title">Definição</h3>
              <p class="info-card-text">
                O microbioma é o conjunto de microrganismos (bactérias, fungos, vírus e protozoários) que habitam o trato gastrointestinal dos animais. Funciona como um <span class="highlight-text">órgão adicional</span> que influencia a saúde, nutrição e performance.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
              <div class="info-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="info-card-title">Impacto no desempenho</h3>
              <p class="info-card-text">
                Um microbioma equilibrado melhora a conversão alimentar, fortalece o sistema imunológico e otimiza a absorção de nutrientes. Estima-se que <span class="highlight-text">até 70% do sistema imunológico</span> está diretamente relacionado ao trato gastrointestinal e seu microbioma.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
              <div class="info-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.94-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93s3.06-7.44 7-7.93v15.86zm2-15.86c1.03.13 2 .45 2.87.93H13v-.93zM13 7h5.24c.25.31.48.65.68 1H13V7zm0 3h6.74c.08.33.15.66.19 1H13v-1zm0 3h6.93c-.06.37-.16.71-.29 1H13v-1zm0 3h6.07c-.44.58-.99 1.1-1.62 1.5H13v-1.5z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="info-card-title">Função biológica</h3>
              <p class="info-card-text">
                O microbioma produz vitaminas, enzimas e ácidos graxos de cadeia curta essenciais para o metabolismo. Funciona como uma <span class="highlight-text">barreira natural</span> contra patógenos e influencia diretamente a saúde intestinal e a eficiência digestiva.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- ROI Benefits Section -->
      <section id="benefits" class="section roi-section section-padding">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">Resultados financeiros mensuráveis</h2>
            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-blue-100">Entenda como a análise do microbioma gera retorno sobre investimento direto</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="roi-cards">
            <div class="roi-card">
              <div class="roi-card-content">
                <div class="roi-percentage">24%</div>
                <h3 class="roi-card-title">Redução de custos com medicamentos</h3>
                <p class="roi-card-text">
                  Um microbioma balanceado reduz significativamente a necessidade de intervenções medicamentosas, especialmente antibióticos. Uma economia direta na compra de medicamentos e redução dos custos operacionais de tratamentos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="roi-card">
              <div class="roi-card-content">
                <div class="roi-percentage">15%</div>
                <h3 class="roi-card-title">Melhora da conversão alimentar</h3>
                <p class="roi-card-text">
                  A otimização do microbioma permite que os animais extraiam mais nutrientes da mesma quantidade de alimento. Isso significa menos ração para o mesmo ganho de peso, representando economia direta no maior custo de produção.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="roi-card">
              <div class="roi-card-content">
                <div class="roi-percentage">35%</div>
                <h3 class="roi-card-title">Redução na mortalidade</h3>
                <p class="roi-card-text">
                  Um sistema imunológico fortalecido pelo microbioma equilibrado reduz significativamente as taxas de mortalidade. Cada animal preservado representa ganho direto no resultado financeiro da operação.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="roi-card">
              <div class="roi-card-content">
                <div class="roi-percentage">20%</div>
                <h3 class="roi-card-title">Maior eficácia de produtos</h3>
                <p class="roi-card-text">
                  Para fabricantes de insumos, a análise de microbioma permite comprovar cientificamente a eficácia dos produtos e criar formulações mais precisas, resultando em maior valor agregado e diferenciação no mercado.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
